high_descs: Walk straight, turn right after the bed to face the desk.
Pick up the cell phone to the left of the alarm clock.
Turn right, turn right at the foot of the bed, turn left at the shelf, turn left to face the side of the bed.
Put the cell phone down on the bed at the edge closest to you.
Walk back over to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone behind the alarm clock.
Walk back over to the side of the bed.
Put the cell phone down on the bed to the left of the cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones to the bed.

high_descs: Walk to the desk to your right.
Grab the phone on the desk.
With the phone, turn around and walk to the bed to your left.
Place the phone on the bed.
Walk to the desk to your left.
Grab the phone on the desk.
With the phone, turn around and walk to the bed to your left.
Place the phone next to the other phone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place two phones on the bed.

high_descs: Walk across the room and turn right and step forward to face the desk.
Pick up the left most media device on the desk.
Turn right and walk around the bed to face the side.
Place the media device on the bed.
Turn left and walk around the bed to the right to face the desk.
Pick up the media device on the desk.
Turn right and walk around the bed to face the side.
Place the media device on the bed next to the other media device.
anns.task_desc: To move two media devices from the desk to the bed.
